WEBVTT

00:49:26.622 --> 00:49:30.065
which is a wonderful resource
for people who want to understand.

00:49:30.089 --> 00:49:33.828
Especially, they've really taken on
some of these controversial topics

00:49:33.852 --> 00:49:35.520
that are often debated,

00:49:35.544 --> 00:49:38.821
and you can read and watch
videos on that website.

00:49:38.845 --> 00:49:41.613
